{
  "stem": "13315.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a Jew, you cannot go much further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Your people like you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They work with you, but I don't know what the others will do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's when I was-- had the possibility to move to California, and to have a defense job as a accountant-- a cost accountant.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Martha moved too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She gave up a very good job there, because there was a jealousy between California and Illinois.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had been a senior chief interviewer with the United States Employment Service in the main office in Chicago.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But here, they didn't want to give her credit for it, just a much lower-- so we said, forget it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She got a job also with the consolidated-- it was a different department-- as security to the assistant director of transportation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we saw then towards the end, in '45, that it was going to end, we were about 40,000 employees.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What would they do with it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So Martha and I talked it over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I first thought we should move to San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she said, look, do you mind very much if we go to Chicago?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mother is not very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you want to go to Chicago?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We go to Chicago.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went to Chicago.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we started all over again.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
